415
00:24:27,850 --> 00:24:29,780
Everyone will move into the dorms.

416
00:24:30,870 --> 00:24:32,200
The more dedicated ones

417
00:24:32,310 --> 00:24:34,230
might even rent a house in Little White House,

418
00:24:34,230 --> 00:24:36,630
