440
00:25:17,990 --> 00:25:19,230
Come in quickly.

441
00:25:19,250 --> 00:25:20,280
Qi.

442
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:22,840
What took you so long?

443
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:24,640
Tianyang.

444
00:25:26,670 --> 00:25:28,550
Xi, long time no see.

445
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:29,630
Long time no see.

446
00:25:29,660 --> 00:25:30,340
I will never forget

447
00:25:30,340 --> 00:25:32,620
