448
00:25:32,620 --> 00:25:33,780
They were so good!

449
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:35,860
I got plenty of sausages here, eat as much as you want.

450
00:25:35,860 --> 00:25:36,390
Thanks.

451
00:25:36,420 --> 00:25:38,150
