452
00:25:38,200 --> 00:25:39,910
They are my friends.

453
00:25:40,300 --> 00:25:41,750
They both call me Xi.

454
00:25:41,770 --> 00:25:44,160
If you don't mind, you can call me Xi too.

455
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:46,040
-Hello, Xi.
-Hello, Xi.

456
00:25:46,050 --> 00:25:47,850
Let me introduce someone to you.

457
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:50,960
He is my partner,

458
00:25:51,270 --> 00:25:52,360
Lin.

459
00:25:52,400 --> 00:25:54,040
You can call him Lin.

460
00:25:54,070 --> 00:25:55,530
-Hello, Lin.
-Hello, Lin.

461
00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:56,540
Hello, everyone.

462
00:25:56,790 --> 00:25:58,850
Lin will show you to your seats.

463
00:25:59,040 --> 00:26:00,200
