466
00:26:06,470 --> 00:26:08,180
Come on in.

467
00:26:10,030 --> 00:26:11,200
Wow.

468
00:26:11,660 --> 00:26:13,110
Enjoy your meal.

469
00:26:13,140 --> 00:26:14,410
I'll go prepare some more.

470
00:26:14,410 --> 00:26:16,340
OK. Thank you, Lin.

471
00:26:18,610 --> 00:26:19,760
-Qi.
-Thank you.

472
00:26:19,790 --> 00:26:21,820
How did you know Xi?

473
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:25,050
He used to be my tutor.

474
00:26:25,090 --> 00:26:26,820
I'm telling you, he's so great.

475
00:26:26,830 --> 00:26:29,280
