484
00:26:47,010 --> 00:26:49,550
You might be 18, but your classmates aren't.

485
00:26:50,490 --> 00:26:51,350
How about this?

486
00:26:51,890 --> 00:26:54,350
Tonight everything's on me

487
00:26:54,910 --> 00:26:56,140
except wine.

488
00:26:56,170 --> 00:26:58,080
Yay!

489
00:26:58,490 --> 00:26:59,790
