493
00:27:04,140 --> 00:27:04,850
Jiang Tian?

494
00:27:05,740 --> 00:27:07,460
Are you in the same class with Jiang Tian?

495
00:27:07,460 --> 00:27:07,950
Yes.

496
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:09,480
You know Tian?

497
00:27:09,500 --> 00:27:11,960
Not just know him, I'm pretty close with him.

498
00:27:15,710 --> 00:27:17,110
