506
00:27:34,310 --> 00:27:35,570
Oh, I remember now.

507
00:27:35,570 --> 00:27:36,990
You dined and dashed?

508
00:27:36,990 --> 00:27:37,820
You didn't pay?

509
00:27:37,820 --> 00:27:38,910
