511
00:27:41,320 --> 00:27:43,090
So you really are close with Tian.

512
00:27:43,090 --> 00:27:45,220
No wonder you come to school together.

513
00:27:48,790 --> 00:27:49,850
Hello, Jiang Tian.

514
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:51,390
Are you really not coming?

515
00:27:51,390 --> 00:27:52,520
Your friend is here,

516
00:27:54,650 --> 00:27:56,250
the one who dined and dashed.

517
00:27:59,780 --> 00:28:00,750
Alright then.

518
00:28:03,980 --> 00:28:05,840
Jiang Tian's busy and can't come.

519
00:28:07,340 --> 00:28:08,840
Enjoy the food and drinks,

520
00:28:08,900 --> 00:28:11,190
and let me know if you need anything.

521
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:14,780
Xi, do you have grilled skewers?

522
00:28:15,330 --> 00:28:15,910
Yes.

523
00:28:16,410 --> 00:28:17,180
Lin,

524
00:28:17,930 --> 00:28:19,060
grill more skewers.

525
00:28:19,080 --> 00:28:20,660
Yes!

526
00:28:20,970 --> 00:28:23,350
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

527
00:28:24,450 --> 00:28:25,650
Eat as much as you can.

528
00:28:36,660 --> 00:28:37,310
Grandpa,

529
00:28:38,320 --> 00:28:39,920
