530
00:28:40,150 --> 00:28:41,570
No, I told you I'm fine.

531
00:28:41,570 --> 00:28:43,060
Why'd you come all the way here?

532
00:28:43,060 --> 00:28:44,690
I just hit my knee,

533
00:28:44,740 --> 00:28:45,340
it's fine.

534
00:28:45,750 --> 00:28:46,830
Alright, stop it.

535
00:28:48,170 --> 00:28:48,910
Let me take a look.

536
00:28:48,910 --> 00:28:50,740
No need.

537
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:52,290
It's nothing.

538
00:28:54,050 --> 00:28:56,210
No big deal.

539
00:28:58,780 --> 00:29:00,610
Are you used to living there?

540
00:29:08,530 --> 00:29:10,540
You never answer my questions.

541
00:29:13,870 --> 00:29:15,760
Are you doing alright?

542
00:29:18,940 --> 00:29:22,400
You know, everything in this world has a cause and effect.

543
00:29:23,490 --> 00:29:24,490
I dried

544
00:29:24,490 --> 00:29:26,380
