546
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:31,440
The fish being eaten, that's the effect.

547
00:29:32,910 --> 00:29:35,490
The cat ate the fish. Easy.

548
00:29:35,490 --> 00:29:36,900
Okay, hang in there.

549
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:38,900
The cat ate the fish being the cause,

550
00:29:39,380 --> 00:29:42,940
and I caught the cat and beat it being the effect.

551
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:45,950
The cat got beaten being the cause,

552
00:29:46,020 --> 00:29:48,610
so it saw me as an enemy.

553
00:29:48,780 --> 00:29:51,370
When I went out, it jumped down and scared me.

554
00:29:51,610 --> 00:29:52,790
That's the effect.

555
00:29:53,090 --> 00:29:55,240
In the end, I bumped my knee.

556
00:29:57,540 --> 00:29:58,750
Many things

557
00:29:58,870 --> 00:30:01,020
seem to be alone,

558
00:30:01,390 --> 00:30:04,420
In fact, they are all closely related.

559
00:30:05,120 --> 00:30:05,900
If you

560
00:30:06,190 --> 00:30:08,530
keep running from your destiny,

561
00:30:09,010 --> 00:30:09,920
you're just

562
00:30:10,450 --> 00:30:12,320
avoiding facing yourself.

563
00:30:18,670 --> 00:30:21,870
Everything happens for a reason,

564
00:30:22,900 --> 00:30:25,070
and it's best to confront it.

565
00:30:26,510 --> 00:30:27,830
What did I tell you?

566
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:31,840
Stay steady

567
00:30:32,570 --> 00:30:34,890
to handle things with ease.

568
00:30:40,330 --> 00:30:41,570
Alright, you sit down.

569
00:30:41,570 --> 00:30:42,390
What?

570
00:30:42,710 --> 00:30:43,910
Let me take care of it.

571
00:30:57,430 --> 00:30:58,380
You made me

572
00:30:58,970 --> 00:31:00,190
bump my knee.

573
00:31:04,080 --> 00:31:04,920
Alright,

574
00:31:04,940 --> 00:31:06,070
I'm not blaming you.

575
00:31:13,150 --> 00:31:14,440
Did you eat my green pepper?

576
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:16,120
You ate what he ate. You have a crush on him?

577
00:31:16,120 --> 00:31:17,540
