Okay. I'll ask someone else.

871
00:52:29,090 --> 00:52:30,460
[Health Room]

872
00:52:40,790 --> 00:52:42,070
It's inappropriate not to go.

873
00:52:42,070 --> 00:52:42,700
I'll go.

874
00:52:42,950 --> 00:52:43,550
OK.

875
00:52:44,340 --> 00:52:45,130
Bye, Tian.

876
00:52:49,250 --> 00:52:51,160
You seem close with Jiang Tian.

877
00:52:51,510 --> 00:52:52,970
Why didn't you invite him?

878
00:52:53,670 --> 00:52:54,940
We're not just close.

879
00:52:55,090 --> 00:52:56,460
We grew up together.

880
00:52:57,870 --> 00:53:00,600
But Tian never participated in such activities.

881
00:53:00,620 --> 00:53:01,500
He is very busy.

882
00:53:02,110 --> 00:53:02,850
Oh.

883
00:53:03,350 --> 00:53:05,750
But I'm surprised that you asked about him.

884
00:53:06,090 --> 00:53:06,950
Why?

885
00:53:07,520 --> 00:53:09,830
Well, you two haven't

886
00:53:09,960 --> 00:53:12,160
gotten along since your first day here.

887
00:53:12,160 --> 00:53:14,830
If Ms. Jing hadn't forced you to be a couple,

888
00:53:15,450 --> 00:53:17,310
you probably wouldn't talk much.

889
00:53:18,250 --> 00:53:21,510
I thought you weren't close and you didn't want him to come.

890
00:53:23,040 --> 00:53:23,610
Yeah,

891
00:53:23,800 --> 00:53:24,750
we're not close

892
00:53:24,790 --> 00:53:25,670
at all.

893
00:53:29,490 --> 00:53:30,860
I'll be home late today.

894
00:53:32,420 --> 00:53:33,290
If my mom asks,

895
00:53:33,320 --> 00:53:35,650
tell her that the teacher wanted to see me.

896
00:53:42,200 --> 00:53:43,550
Not close at all?

897
00:53:43,960 --> 00:53:45,380
He even let you know his schedule.

